{"tid":962072,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人想賺$31500？","createTime":"2018-12-30T14:57:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-01T00:39:16.000Z","uid":179902,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2163fe81673278dcf7ac12dd218ca470436a193d","tid":962072,"uid":179902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T14:57:08.000Z","msg":"【招募臨床研究志願者】<br />\n<br />\n&bull; 香港中文大學一期臨床研究中心現正招募健康人仕參與一項稱為 RO7020531 之藥物的研究（也稱為臨床試驗）。RO7020531 被研究用於用於乙型肝炎病毒所引致的肝臟疾病的治療。<br />\n<br />\n&bull; 招募對象: 18-60歲的男性及女性，甄選檢查證明健康狀況良好。<br />\n<br />\n&bull; 參與研究你要做些什麼: 到研究中心進行健康檢查、服食研究藥物、留院(15日14夜)觀察及覆診(1次)。如有需要，您可能被邀請進行額外的覆診。<br />\n<br />\n&bull; 研究補償: 您將會在完成研究後獲得港幣 $31,500 的現金津貼，以補助您因參與本研究所付出的時間、所造成的不便或因參與本研究而付出的合理開支。<br />\n<br />\n&bull; 可能的風險: 您可能因本研究中使用的藥物或程序而出現副作用。RO7020531和類似的另一種化合物主要報告的副作用包括：可能出現過敏反應、類流感症狀（身體不適）、疲倦、頭痛、噁心、嘔吐、發燒和發冷、肌肉疼痛、腹痛和流鼻血。一些自願者的白血球和血小板減少，凝血時間加長。在終止後這些副作用得以緩解。<br />\n<br />\n&bull; 如何參與研究: 有意參與者請致電一期臨床研究中心(Phase 1 Clinical Trial Centre)了解詳情(電話: 3505 3377, 9am&ndash;5pm)或到一期臨床研究中心網站登記 (<a href=\"http://www.p1ctc.med.cuhk.edu.hk/Apps/VolunteerTC2.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.p1ctc.med.cuhk.edu.hk%2FApps%2FVolunteerTC2.aspx&d=e82WoVn8nbkphjqdeXFk1k%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=4c4cc76e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.p1ctc.med.cuhk.edu.hk/Apps/VolunteerTC2.aspx</a>)。"},{"pid":"8455ffc6ec26c166862ed2b9b8d8a785df71d5e9","tid":962072,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T15:14:09.000Z","msg":"少個香爐少隻鬼"},{"pid":"8059bdc35e4cb92217cb016f1de88a9a411b18de","tid":962072,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T15:15:35.000Z","msg":"攞條命比佢試，不了"},{"pid":"aa38a634bdd31888636d486ddd4b716ed5ffc3f4","tid":962072,"uid":223328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T15:19:13.000Z","msg":"試完奶野佢唔包<br />\n做人做狗自己諗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2536f00274d2b622af7ec7fa03418b71688da6d5","tid":962072,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T15:20:42.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"a37524378a773ae7976caabe652b1590165d7c85","tid":962072,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T15:24:47.000Z","msg":"姐係食咩藥？"},{"pid":"a63aa51fbf39b78e62f8e404509b62d274d7b5df","tid":962072,"uid":151196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T15:29:19.000Z","msg":"$31500 不了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7970935bc1b9d035d1b58f083b40387a1fc217e","tid":962072,"uid":21156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa38a634bdd31888636d486ddd4b716ed5ffc3f4","tid":962072,"uid":223328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T15:19:13.000Z","msg":"試完奶野佢唔包<br />\n做人做狗自己諗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T21:24:53.000Z","msg":"請問可以講清楚d，咩人奶過野？之後又點？謝"},{"pid":"d6989fa3e6c121a20b0ea500d0d005e34bfe11f6","tid":962072,"uid":15935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T21:31:03.000Z","msg":"個post出咗好耐，睇嚟無水魚中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽講試完藥奶嘢嘅話，佢地理撚得你死，唔會執手尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3160845a1a92014047d27f3d51263a1f50169cd5","tid":962072,"uid":164980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T21:31:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8956ceb07f8ef87bfb6a8bb5583fe5f0643e4763","tid":962072,"uid":71748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T00:31:28.000Z","msg":"唔係十一月完左啦咩？<br />\n<br />\n坐監都起碼可以去下操場果度得病房同好細既活動室"},{"pid":"d900e1b51085cd